snippet.title: Amber Heard shines in a golden strapless gown at the 2018 AMAs
snippet.description:
She's a Hollywood favorite. And Amber Heard looked absolutely radiant during Tuesday night's American Music Awards at the Microsoft Theater in LA. The Aquaman actress dazzled the red carpet wearing a black and gold number which expertly highlighted her slim stems.
